ABOUT

Karoka is led by Louise du Plessis, an experienced English educator with 30 years of teaching across three countries and educational systems.

Louise's career includes 7 years as a certified South African secondary school English teacher, 14 years as a certified Advanced Skills secondary school English teacher in the United Kingdom, and 9 years teaching middle and secondary school English in the French education system.

This international expertise and deep understanding of diverse educational frameworks ensures every student receives instruction tailored to their unique needs and goals.

CV available upon request.
